S{To effects of large doses, Vegetable acids, infusion of galls, or green tea, R[Coff], R[Hyos] to effects of small doses, R[Camph], R[Coff], R[Hep], R[Hyos], R[Op], R[Puls], R[Sabad] (salivation), Vinum. }

